import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch } from "react-router-dom"
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"

import Login from './newComponents/login/login.component'
import Landing from './newComponents/landing/landing.component'

function newApp () {
  return(
    <Router>
      <Switch>
      <Route exact path="/">
          <Landing />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/student/home">
          <StudentApp />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/instructor/home">
          <InstructorApp />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/instructor">
          <Instructor />
        </Route>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default newApp
